<sync start=369198>
<p class=KRCC>뭐가?
<sync start=371498>&nbsp;
<sync start=373536>
<p class=KRCC>위스키야..
<sync start=376536>&nbsp;
<sync start=378875>
<p class=KRCC>기다리고 기다리던 울덜 꿈이..
<sync start=384747>
